{"tid":1439810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭神器「臭雞蛋」","createTime":"2019-08-10T08:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T08:33:10.000Z","uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"28a108333735725e1c31302b1d515ffa7c259b20","tid":1439810,"uid":300510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:33:10.000Z","msg":"致前線義士：<br />\n兩個月嘅抗爭，政府毫無回應，原因係背靠黑警無後果的暴力執法，<br />\n一旦黑警放下全副武裝，就等於喪失暴力執法的能力。<br />\n<br />\n至於如何令黑警「解甲」？<br />\n可請參考以下故事<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">伊索寓言《風和太陽》</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/g9e6yle.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Fg9e6yle.html&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=7e3581e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/news/g9e6yle.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【結論】<br />\n磚頭硬物並不能有效阻止配備全副武裝嘅防暴隊和速龍，<br />\n反而污染咗果班痴撚線嘅黑警裝備，才能有效應對！<br />\n識玩一定係玩「臭雞蛋」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">噁心的臭蛋</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://elite0905.pixnet.net/blog/post/25928800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Felite0905.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F25928800&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=ba2358a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://elite0905.pixnet.net/blog/post/25928800</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎硏究討論[url][/url]"}]}